<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>245</hymn_number>
<author>Runchawng</author>
<title>Lal Nunnem Lenna</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mubang ka ngai ka lal nunnem lenna,
 Lautha, Jordan ei pui kai in;
 Nitum lohna gam ei tunin.

[V2]
 Aw, mitin nawpna pielgal ninnuom,
 Lungsietna zam vel nuoia chun,
 Lili pak hawih lunna gamah.

[V3]
 2. Thepna ngomei chu a hung zam vel ie,
 Mithieng te lailenna mun chu;
 Tunkal ka ngaklah ngei ie aw !

[V4]
 3. Pak bang tuoi hen nuoi simlei gimum hi,
 Ei hung puiin aw, Lal Isu;
 Zan um lohna Na gama chun.

[V5]
 4. Aw, zemun chu kei le ka tun tieng leh,
 Ka umna hi ngai ta puong ie;
 Nunnuom in ngabang leng tang ka.</lyrics>
</song>